{"tid":747191,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"港男正垃圾！廢柴之中你地都算係極品","createTime":"2018-07-18T07:44:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T17:20:40.000Z","uid":137017,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a4f447dcb374959b732f9aa29e82cb591374b1e9","tid":747191,"uid":137017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:44:17.000Z","msg":"對住白皮豬騷擾你女朋友都唔敢打柒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你哋有咩價值?仲喺度討論會唔會俾人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見到白皮豬騷擾你女朋友就應該大大力打柒佢，佢哋嘅生命賤過地底泥，你驚佢拍片咪連佢台機、記憶卡都打爆囉！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n問心嗰句，男朋友我都會揀香港人，但唔係香港懦夫。對住不公義又唔敢講，對住欺負你嘅人又唔敢出聲，你哋唔覺好廢嘅咩？"},{"pid":"ceb48e7e762a07321e040fb15fdc5ddab8a6a811","tid":747191,"uid":26451,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T10:07:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0438b85d1e6d7193d5d9b6dfe09cf84ba9f7c198","tid":747191,"uid":137017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T13:15:40.000Z","msg":"淨係夠膽留負評，冇鬼用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f680490792ce88f136c20b92dff8e627cddb5a42","tid":747191,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T13:43:04.000Z","msg":"香港女又好叻咩?剩係識住享其成"},{"pid":"178e5dd6342fea3d2b6bfd640f5e0cd7adb7b356","tid":747191,"uid":70596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ceb48e7e762a07321e040fb15fdc5ddab8a6a811","tid":747191,"uid":26451,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T10:07:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T11:28:10.000Z","msg":"夫目前犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e7252db87ee91ba7cff20f6e50ee8e69cd1f900","tid":747191,"uid":46584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T17:02:44.000Z","msg":"樓豬一定冇女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj